<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmi:id="-OKTeeSNqeT44xeZuunHOMQ" name="plan_for_risk_red,_XVBmEJExEeCnTdC8bcBfaw" guid="-OKTeeSNqeT44xeZuunHOMQ" changeDate="2011-06-27T10:57:17.468-0700">
  <sections xmi:id="_AbLO4KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Identify key project hazards" guid="_AbLO4KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>Hazards, in this context, are project conditions you wish to avoid, such as an implementation that does not meet its QoS&#xD;
requirements. This step identifies likely project hazards.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_CAgN8KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Determine likelihood of key project hazards" guid="_CAgN8KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>The likelihood of the hazard is multiplied by its severity to compute the project risk. Hazards with likelihoods above a&#xD;
certain threshold should be explicitly mitigated by one or more risk mitigation activities.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_EgrrsKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Compute key project risks" guid="_EgrrsKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>Risk = likelihood x severity, for each project hazard.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_FpQdUKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Rank project risks" guid="_FpQdUKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>Hazards should be ranked by risk so that the most critical ones may be addressed.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_GzA6sKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Specify risk mitigation activities for key project risks" guid="_GzA6sKDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>A risk mitigation activity is a work task whose specific goal is to clarify a project risk.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_JEmi0KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q" name="Capture the risk management aspects" guid="_JEmi0KDnEeC3BtbOsE9k9Q">
    <sectionDescription>Capture&amp;nbsp;all of the project's risk-related details.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>The purpose of this task is to identify and prioritize project risks and how they will be handled, and capture this&#xD;
information in the risk management plan.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
